I think religion has changed (all religion) because of technology and we don’t need to read bones to check the weather or check entrails to see where to plant our crops these days. I could kill my dog and call it whatever I want religion is a beleif of Many and they are free to follow it!<br>
<br>
I get people all the time that bring up the statement you said in your last post and I say to them well you used to burn witches? And you slaughtered the Muslims to “bring Christianity” to them and you know what cracks me up they say “OH NO” there is know way they where Christians. Umm… sorry I think they called them a HOLY CRUSADE? <br>
<br>
I am not up for a debate I just don’t like when people bring up the past and think that is how we are today. I think it falls down to ignorance on both sides.  <br>
<br>
Yes the early whites had slaves (but I should not have to pay for that), yes the Christians burned witches but I don’t go knocking on the relatives of salam, yes the Christians “slaughtered” the Muslims during the holy crusades but that does not mean the Christian today has to pay for this slaughter. <br>
<br>
I guess at times I get defensive because its like being a square peg in a round society. Tell someone your are a witch and OMG you have just turned into SATAN.  I am sorry but I think that %50 of the Christian church is ignorant of the fact there was the divine WAY before their god and there will be the divine when there GOD ceases to exist.  The Egyptian gods where here for thousands and thousands of years the Christian god has been here for what? 2 or 3k so there is a lot of time left.<br>
<br>
Remember people above else we are HUMAN FIRST! I am not going to take your kid for my next holiday celebration.  Please don’t try and save me or convert me to a GOD I do not believe in. <br>
<br>
Do not fear what you do not understand!<br>
